{
  "video_id": "-hY9QSdaReY",
  "title": "How a blind astronomer found a way to hear the stars | Wanda Diaz Merced",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13163.0,
      "end_time": 15429.0,
      "text": "Once there was a star."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16820.0,
      "end_time": 18804.0,
      "text": "Like everything else, she was born;"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18828.0,
      "end_time": 22609.0,
      "text": "grew to be around 30 times the mass of our sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22633.0,
      "end_time": 24926.0,
      "text": "and lived for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25475.0,
      "end_time": 26843.0,
      "text": "Exactly how long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26867.0,
      "end_time": 28606.0,
      "text": "people cannot really tell."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29162.0,
      "end_time": 30941.0,
      "text": "Just like everything in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30965.0,
      "end_time": 34414.0,
      "text": "she reached the end of her regular star days"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34438.0,
      "end_time": 37150.0,
      "text": "when her heart, the core of her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37390.0,
      "end_time": 38505.0,
      "text": "exhausted its fuel."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38905.0,
      "end_time": 40212.0,
      "text": "But that was no end."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40236.0,
      "end_time": 43762.0,
      "text": "She transformed into a supernova, and in the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43786.0,
      "end_time": 46440.0,
      "text": "releasing a tremendous amount of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46464.0,
      "end_time": 49172.0,
      "text": "outshining the rest of the galaxy"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49196.0,
      "end_time": 51530.0,
      "text": "and emitting, in one second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51554.0,
      "end_time": 55627.0,
      "text": "the same amount of energy our sun will release in 10 days."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55651.0,
      "end_time": 58922.0,
      "text": "And she evolved into another role in our galaxy."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59783.0,
      "end_time": 62257.0,
      "text": "Supernova explosions are very extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62638.0,
      "end_time": 66858.0,
      "text": "But the ones that emit gamma rays are even more extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67417.0,
      "end_time": 69706.0,
      "text": "In the process of becoming a supernova,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69730.0,
      "end_time": 73153.0,
      "text": "the interior of the star collapses under its own weight"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73177.0,
      "end_time": 76650.0,
      "text": "and it starts rotating ever faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76890.0,
      "end_time": 79954.0,
      "text": "like an ice skater when pulling their arms in close to their body."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80592.0,
      "end_time": 85500.0,
      "text": "In that way, it starts rotating very fast and it increases, powerfully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85740.0,
      "end_time": 86634.0,
      "text": "its magnetic field."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87110.0,
      "end_time": 90100.0,
      "text": "The matter around the star is dragged around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90124.0,
      "end_time": 93442.0,
      "text": "and some energy from that rotation is transferred to that matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93466.0,
      "end_time": 96874.0,
      "text": "and the magnetic field is increased even further."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97477.0,
      "end_time": 103239.0,
      "text": "In that way, our star had extra energy to outshine the rest of the galaxy"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103263.0,
      "end_time": 105566.0,
      "text": "in brightness and gamma ray emission."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106119.0,
      "end_time": 108608.0,
      "text": "My star, the one in my story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108632.0,
      "end_time": 111280.0,
      "text": "became what is known as a magnetar."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111304.0,
      "end_time": 112985.0,
      "text": "And just for your information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113900.0,
      "end_time": 116890.0,
      "text": "the magnetic field of a magnetar is 1,000 trillion times"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116914.0,
      "end_time": 118683.0,
      "text": "the magnetic field of Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119953.0,
      "end_time": 122609.0,
      "text": "The most energetic events ever measured by astronomers"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122633.0,
      "end_time": 124887.0,
      "text": "carry the name gamma-ray bursts"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124912.0,
      "end_time": 128519.0,
      "text": "because we observe them as bursts most or explosions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128543.0,
      "end_time": 131760.0,
      "text": "most strongly measured as gamma-ray light."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131886.0,
      "end_time": 136910.0,
      "text": "Our star, like the one in our story that became a magnetar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136115.0,
      "end_time": 138186.0,
      "text": "is detected as a gamma-ray burst"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138210.0,
      "end_time": 140770.0,
      "text": "during the most energetic portion of the explosion."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142167.0,
      "end_time": 147468.0,
      "text": "Yet, even though gamma-ray bursts are the strongest events"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147492.0,
      "end_time": 149581.0,
      "text": "ever measured by astronomers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149605.0,
      "end_time": 152242.0,
      "text": "we cannot see them with our naked eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152266.0,
      "end_time": 154594.0,
      "text": "We depend, we rely on other methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154618.0,
      "end_time": 157406.0,
      "text": "in order to study this gamma-ray light."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157431.0,
      "end_time": 159278.0,
      "text": "We cannot see them with our naked eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159302.0,
      "end_time": 162372.0,
      "text": "We can only see an itty bitty, tiny portion"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162396.0,
      "end_time": 166122.0,
      "text": "of the electromagnetic spectrum that we call visible light."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 166146.0,
      "end_time": 168417.0,
      "text": "And beyond that, we rely on other methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168442.0,
      "end_time": 173702.0,
      "text": "Yet as astronomers, we study a wider range of light"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173726.0,
      "end_time": 176490.0,
      "text": "and we depend on other methods to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176514.0,
      "end_time": 179900.0,
      "text": "On the screen, it may look like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179812.0,
      "end_time": 181544.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re seeing a plot."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181568.0,
      "end_time": 183493.0,
      "text": "That is a light curve."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183517.0,
      "end_time": 187660.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a plot of intensity of light over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187900.0,
      "end_time": 189554.0,
      "text": "It is a gamma-ray light curve."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190130.0,
      "end_time": 193705.0,
      "text": "Sighted astronomers depend on this kind of plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193729.0,
      "end_time": 198401.0,
      "text": "in order to interpret how this light intensity changes over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198933.0,
      "end_time": 204448.0,
      "text": "On the left, you will be seeing the light intensity without a burst,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204473.0,
      "end_time": 208628.0,
      "text": "and on the right, you will be seeing the light intensity with the burst."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210381.0,
      "end_time": 214820.0,
      "text": "Early during my career, I could also see this kind of plot."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 214562.0,
      "end_time": 217290.0,
      "text": "But then, I lost my sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217314.0,
      "end_time": 220465.0,
      "text": "I completely lost my sight because of extended illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220490.0,
      "end_time": 224175.0,
      "text": "and with it, I lost the opportunity to see this plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 225208.0,
      "end_time": 227965.0,
      "text": "and the opportunity to do my physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229672.0,
      "end_time": 232127.0,
      "text": "It was a very strong transition for me in many ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233295.0,
      "end_time": 237540.0,
      "text": "And professionally, it left me without a way to do my science."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237564.0,
      "end_time": 242179.0,
      "text": "I longed to access and scrutinize this energetic light"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242203.0,
      "end_time": 244889.0,
      "text": "and figure out the astrophysical cause."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 244913.0,
      "end_time": 248375.0,
      "text": "I wanted to experience the spacious wonder, the excitement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248399.0,
      "end_time": 252848.0,
      "text": "the joy produced by the detection of such a titanic celestial event."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253352.0,
      "end_time": 256652.0,
      "text": "I thought long and hard about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 256676.0,
      "end_time": 260361.0,
      "text": "when I suddenly realized that all a light curve is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 260385.0,
      "end_time": 264226.0,
      "text": "is a table of numbers converted into a visual plot."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264861.0,
      "end_time": 266762.0,
      "text": "So along with my collaborators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266786.0,
      "end_time": 270994.0,
      "text": "we worked really hard and we translated the numbers into sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 271765.0,
      "end_time": 273769.0,
      "text": "I achieved access to the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273793.0,
      "end_time": 278806.0,
      "text": "and today I&#39;m able to do physics at the level of the best astronomer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278830.0,
      "end_time": 279981.0,
      "text": "using sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 280500.0,
      "end_time": 282633.0,
      "text": "And what people have been able to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 282657.0,
      "end_time": 283810.0,
      "text": "mainly visually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283834.0,
      "end_time": 285178.0,
      "text": "for hundreds of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285202.0,
      "end_time": 287544.0,
      "text": "now I do it using sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287892.0,
      "end_time": 288929.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288953.0,
      "end_time": 290655.0,
      "text": "Listening to this gamma-ray burst"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 290679.0,
      "end_time": 292998.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re seeing on the -- (Applause continues)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293230.0,
      "end_time": 294174.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 294198.0,
      "end_time": 296906.0,
      "text": "Listening to this burst that you&#39;re seeing on the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 296930.0,
      "end_time": 299525.0,
      "text": "brought something to the ear beyond the obvious burst."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 299973.0,
      "end_time": 301908.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m going to play the burst for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301932.0,
      "end_time": 303986.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not music, it&#39;s sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 305264.0,
      "end_time": 308515.0,
      "text": "(Digital beeping sounds)"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308539.0,
      "end_time": 311830.0,
      "text": "This is scientific data converted into sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311854.0,
      "end_time": 313870.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s mapped in pitch."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313112.0,
      "end_time": 315531.0,
      "text": "The process is called sonification."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318958.0,
      "end_time": 321268.0,
      "text": "So listening to this brought something to the ear"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 321292.0,
      "end_time": 322640.0,
      "text": "besides the obvious burst."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 322665.0,
      "end_time": 327186.0,
      "text": "When I examine the very strong low-frequency regions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 327210.0,
      "end_time": 332820.0,
      "text": "or bass line -- I&#39;m zooming into the bass line now."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 333500.0,
      "end_time": 339190.0,
      "text": "We noted resonances characteristic of electrically charged gasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 339430.0,
      "end_time": 340645.0,
      "text": "like the solar wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340669.0,
      "end_time": 343171.0,
      "text": "And I want you to hear what I heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343196.0,
      "end_time": 346977.0,
      "text": "You will hear it as a very fast decrease in volume."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347100.0,
      "end_time": 349763.0,
      "text": "And because you&#39;re sighted, I&#39;m giving you a red line"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 349788.0,
      "end_time": 353727.0,
      "text": "indicating what intensity of light is being converted into sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 355672.0,
      "end_time": 358860.0,
      "text": "(Digital hum and whistling sound)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 358110.0,
      "end_time": 361404.0,
      "text": "The (Whistles) is frogs at home, don&#39;t pay attention to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361428.0,
      "end_time": 363274.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 363298.0,
      "end_time": 368525.0,
      "text": "(Digital hum and whistling sound)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 368549.0,
      "end_time": 370421.0,
      "text": "I think you heard it, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371503.0,
      "end_time": 372780.0,
      "text": "So what we found"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 372804.0,
      "end_time": 377717.0,
      "text": "is that the bursts last long enough in order to support wave resonances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377742.0,
      "end_time": 381959.0,
      "text": "which are things caused by exchanges of energy between particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381983.0,
      "end_time": 383301.0,
      "text": "that may have been excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 383325.0,
      "end_time": 384705.0,
      "text": "that depend on the volume."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 385151.0,
      "end_time": 388241.0,
      "text": "You may remember that I said that the matter around the star"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 388265.0,
      "end_time": 389921.0,
      "text": "is dragged around?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 389945.0,
      "end_time": 393759.0,
      "text": "It transmits power with frequency and field distribution"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 393783.0,
      "end_time": 395505.0,
      "text": "determined by the dimensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 396434.0,
      "end_time": 400384.0,
      "text": "You may remember that we were talking about a super-massive star"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 400408.0,
      "end_time": 403576.0,
      "text": "that became a very strong magnetic field magnetar."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 404264.0,
      "end_time": 408637.0,
      "text": "If this is the case, then outflows from the exploding star"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 408661.0,
      "end_time": 411144.0,
      "text": "may be associated with this gamma-ray burst."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 411168.0,
      "end_time": 412736.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 412760.0,
      "end_time": 415727.0,
      "text": "That star formation may be a very important part"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 415751.0,
      "end_time": 417265.0,
      "text": "of these supernova explosions."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 418470.0,
      "end_time": 422434.0,
      "text": "Listening to this very gamma-ray burst brought us to the notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 422458.0,
      "end_time": 425257.0,
      "text": "that the use of sound as an adjunctive visual display"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 425281.0,
      "end_time": 427506.0,
      "text": "may also support sighted astronomers"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 427530.0,
      "end_time": 429979.0,
      "text": "in the search for more information in the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 430562.0,
      "end_time": 435880.0,
      "text": "Simultaneously, I worked on analyzing measurements from other telescopes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 435904.0,
      "end_time": 438107.0,
      "text": "and my experiments demonstrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438131.0,
      "end_time": 442344.0,
      "text": "that when you use sound as an adjunctive visual display,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 442369.0,
      "end_time": 445285.0,
      "text": "astronomers can find more information"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 445309.0,
      "end_time": 448176.0,
      "text": "in this now more accessible data set."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 449860.0,
      "end_time": 452830.0,
      "text": "This ability to transform data into sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 452854.0,
      "end_time": 455931.0,
      "text": "gives astronomy a tremendous power of transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456381.0,
      "end_time": 460321.0,
      "text": "And the fact that a field that is so visual may be improved"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 460346.0,
      "end_time": 465190.0,
      "text": "in order to include anyone with interest in understanding what lies in the heavens"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 465430.0,
      "end_time": 466552.0,
      "text": "is a spirit-lifter."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 467390.0,
      "end_time": 469279.0,
      "text": "When I lost my sight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 469303.0,
      "end_time": 471379.0,
      "text": "I noticed that I didn&#39;t have access"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 471403.0,
      "end_time": 474290.0,
      "text": "to the same amount and quality of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474530.0,
      "end_time": 475449.0,
      "text": "a sighted astronomer had."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476220.0,
      "end_time": 479700.0,
      "text": "It was not until we innovated with the sonification process"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 479724.0,
      "end_time": 483676.0,
      "text": "that I regained the hope to be a productive member of the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 483700.0,
      "end_time": 486310.0,
      "text": "that I had worked so hard to be part of."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 487429.0,
      "end_time": 491880.0,
      "text": "Yet, information access is not the only area in astronomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 491904.0,
      "end_time": 494880.0,
      "text": "where this is important."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494602.0,
      "end_time": 497126.0,
      "text": "The situation is systemic"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 497150.0,
      "end_time": 500119.0,
      "text": "and scientific fields are not keeping up."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 500825.0,
      "end_time": 503477.0,
      "text": "The body is something changeable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 503501.0,
      "end_time": 506866.0,
      "text": "anyone may develop a disability at any point."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 506890.0,
      "end_time": 509128.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s think about, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 509152.0,
      "end_time": 511938.0,
      "text": "scientists that are already at the top of their careers."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 511963.0,
      "end_time": 514803.0,
      "text": "What happens to them if they develop a disability?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 514827.0,
      "end_time": 517244.0,
      "text": "Will they feel excommunicated as I did?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 517839.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521290.00000000006,
      "text": "Information access empowers us to flourish."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 521499.0,
      "end_time": 525990.0,
      "text": "It gives us equal opportunities to display our talents"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 525123.0,
      "end_time": 527986.0,
      "text": "and choose what we want to do with our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 528100.0,
      "end_time": 531318.0,
      "text": "based on interest and not based on potential barriers."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 532294.0,
      "end_time": 536661.0,
      "text": "When we give people the opportunity to succeed without limits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 536685.0,
      "end_time": 541242.0,
      "text": "that will lead to personal fulfillment and prospering life."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 541267.0,
      "end_time": 543700.0,
      "text": "And I think that the use of sound in astronomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543724.0,
      "end_time": 547201.0,
      "text": "is helping us to achieve that and to contribute to science."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548119.0,
      "end_time": 552651.0,
      "text": "While other countries told me that the study of perception techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 552675.0,
      "end_time": 556252.0,
      "text": "in order to study astronomy data is not relevant to astronomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 556276.0,
      "end_time": 559476.0,
      "text": "because there are no blind astronomers in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 559500.0,
      "end_time": 562904.0,
      "text": "South Africa said, \"We want people with disabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 562928.0,
      "end_time": 564904.0,
      "text": "to contribute to the field.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 564928.0,
      "end_time": 566254.0,
      "text": "Right now, I&#39;m working"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 566278.0,
      "end_time": 569100.0,
      "text": "at the South African Astronomical Observatory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 569340.0,
      "end_time": 572119.0,
      "text": "at the Office of Astronomy for Development."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 572436.0,
      "end_time": 577177.0,
      "text": "There, we are working on sonification techniques and analysis methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 577201.0,
      "end_time": 580647.0,
      "text": "to impact the students of the Athlone School for the Blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 581603.0,
      "end_time": 584890.0,
      "text": "These students will be learning radio astronomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 584113.0,
      "end_time": 587351.0,
      "text": "and they will be learning the sonification methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 587375.0,
      "end_time": 591846.0,
      "text": "in order to study astronomical events like huge ejections of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 591870.0,
      "end_time": 594306.0,
      "text": "from the sun, known as coronal mass ejections."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 595194.0,
      "end_time": 596953.0,
      "text": "What we learn with these students --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 596977.0,
      "end_time": 600774.0,
      "text": "these students have multiple disabilities and coping strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 600798.0,
      "end_time": 602674.0,
      "text": "that will be accommodated --"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 602698.0,
      "end_time": 605537.0,
      "text": "what we learn with these students will directly impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 605561.0,
      "end_time": 608718.0,
      "text": "the way things are being done at the professional level."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 608742.0,
      "end_time": 610800.0,
      "text": "I humbly call this development."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 610825.0,
      "end_time": 613810.0,
      "text": "And this is happening right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 614350.0,
      "end_time": 617728.0,
      "text": "I think that science is for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 618275.0,
      "end_time": 619723.0,
      "text": "It belongs to the people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 619747.0,
      "end_time": 621997.0,
      "text": "and it has to be available to everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 622220.0,
      "end_time": 624235.0,
      "text": "because we are all natural explorers."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 624956.0,
      "end_time": 630136.0,
      "text": "I think that if we limit people with disabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 630171.0,
      "end_time": 632000.0,
      "text": "from participating in science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 632240.0,
      "end_time": 635672.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll sever our links with history and with society."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 635696.0,
      "end_time": 639142.0,
      "text": "I dream of a level scientific playing field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 639166.0,
      "end_time": 644154.0,
      "text": "where people encourage respect and respect each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 644178.0,
      "end_time": 647266.0,
      "text": "where people exchange strategies and discover together."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 647810.0,
      "end_time": 652107.0,
      "text": "If people with disabilities are allowed into the scientific field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 652131.0,
      "end_time": 656839.0,
      "text": "an explosion, a huge titanic burst of knowledge will take place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 656864.0,
      "end_time": 658341.0,
      "text": "I am sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 661251.0,
      "end_time": 663100.0,
      "text": "(Digital beeping sounds)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663124.0,
      "end_time": 664988.0,
      "text": "That is the titanic burst."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 666420.0,
      "end_time": 667570.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 667595.0,
      "end_time": 668746.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 668770.0,
      "end_time": 674442.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}